libgalago: libgalago (Galago Presence Framework)
libgalago:
libgalago: Galago is a desktop presence framework, designed to transmit presence 
libgalago: information between programs. To put it in simpler terms, it takes 
libgalago: information on who is online and their away/idle states from an instant 
libgalago: messenger (such as pidgin) or other similar programs and lets other 
libgalago: programs (such as Evolution) to make use of it.  The advantage of such 
libgalago: a framework is that it brings your programs closer together. When you 
libgalago: receive an e-mail from a friend who is in your buddy list, you'll be 
libgalago: able to immediately tell their online status, for example. 
libgalago:
